Superboy and the Legion of Super-Heroes #244
Publisher:  DC Comics
Publication Date:  October 1978

Writer:  Paul Levitz
Penciler:  Joe Staton
Inker:  Joe Giella
Letterer:  Ben Oda
Colorist:  Cory Adams
Editor:  Al Milgrom 

The Dark Circle are revealed to be behind the war between the Khunds and Earth. The Legion of Super-Heroes do their best to defend Earth and to stop the Dark Circle. Meanwhile, Mordru reveals himself to be a manipulator in the war as a means of revenge against the Legion.

